                <div class="detail-item">
                  <i class="fas fa-palette" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                  <span>Black/Green</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p class="vehicle-description">
                Experience extreme power with the 2021 Grave Digger Monster Truck, built with massive 66-inch tires and a fully custom suspension system. This iconic black-and-green beast is powered by a high-performance supercharged engine.
              </p>

              <a href="/inv/detail/15" class="view-details">
                <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                <span>View Full Details</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </section>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>